### 1 — Create an invoice
POST http://localhost:3000/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: dev-key-change-me

{
    "invoice_id": "INV-001",
    "customer": "Acme Corp",
    "amount": 1500.00,
    "due_date": "2026-05-31"
}

### 2 — Fetch it back
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices/INV-001/status
x-api-key: dev-key-change-me

### 3 — Try without an API key (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices/INV-001/status

### 4 — Try with bad data (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: dev-key-change-me

{
    "customer": "Acme Corp"
}

