### 7 — Reference match: clean win, invoice auto-closes
POST http://localhost:3000/payments
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: dev-key-change-me

{
    "payment_id": "PAY-001",
    "payer_name": "Tony Stark",
    "amount": 2000.00,
    "reference": "INV-REF-001",
    "payment_date": "2026-04-27"
}

### 8 — Fuzzy match: requires_review true, invoice stays open
POST http://localhost:3000/payments
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: dev-key-change-me

{
    "payment_id": "PAY-002",
    "payer_name": "Globex Internationnal",
    "amount": 850.00,
    "payment_date": "2026-04-27"
}

